  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to KWidgetsAddons</title>

    <para>
      The <application>KWidgetsAddons</application> package contains a library
      that contains add-on widgets and classes for applications that use the
      Qt Widgets module.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

